This is Xaric, a client for the Internet Relay Chat system. 
For more information about IRC, try <http://www.irchelp.org>

For installation instructions, read the INSTALL file.

More information about xaric can be found in the doc/ directory.


Mail suggestions and bug reports to laeos@ptw.com

